            <t t-translation="off">
                
                ^FX reset all memory
                ^MCY
                ^JUR
                
                ^XA

                ^FX Top section with logo, name and address.
                ^FX begin logo in binary

                ^FX end logo in binary
                ^FO50,220^GB700,3,3^FS

